1
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,719
Xiaomo,

2
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,519
you used the private child to embarrass me

3
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,280
in front of the media,

4
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,400
and you even want money.

5
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:41,519
If I don't give you money,

6
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,319
we'll die together.

7
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,359
Chu Tianxiang,

8
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:47,120
I will ruin your reputation.

9
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,519
Bastard,

10
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,079
it's all your fault.

11
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,519
It's all your fault.

12
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,840
It's all your fault.

13
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,040
Stop crying.

14
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,799
Xiaomo.

15
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,319
I...

16
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,640
I know I was wrong.

17
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,520
Long time no see.

18
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,960
It's been 20 years.

19
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,120
Mom.

20
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:18,000
Mom, don't leave me. Mom.

21
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,599
Mom,

22
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:27,759
don't leave me. Mom, save me.

23
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:39,919
They are the ones who deserve to die.

24
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,800
I... I know I was wrong.

25
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:51,039
I really know I was wrong.

26
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:52,439
I...

27
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:54,639
You...

28
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:57,879
Can you forgive me?

29
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,120
You are not wrong.

30
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,319
You are just scared.

31
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,280
You're afraid of getting old and losing your looks,

32
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:12,280
and no one will take care of you in your old age.

33
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:15,199
If you're counting on me,

34
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,840
you'd better give up on that idea.

35
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,560
No,

36
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,080
I want to treat you well.

37
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,080
I really want to treat you well this time.

38
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:29,599
Get lost.

39
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,240
[A car accident occurred on West Second Street.]

40
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,360
[One person died on the spot.]

41
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,519
[It is reported that the victim is Lin Yu,]

42
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,600
[who was recently released from prison.]

43
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,079
Who is Lin Yu?

44
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:39,560
Chumo's mother.

45
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,399
Sorry to keep you waiting.

46
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,040
I bought some steak.

47
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,040
Let's have steak for dinner.

48
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,519
I'll go cook it.

49
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,319
Wait a moment.

50
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,480
You're not going to jump off a building, are you?

51
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:45,360
If you want to accompany her on her last journey,

52
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:46,839
I can go with you.

53
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,079
Do you know why your father

54
00:06:50,079 --> 00:06:50,839
doesn't let you

55
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:52,319
handle the core tasks of the group?

56
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:55,319
Because you are kind.

57
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,000
Kind to the point of foolishness,

58
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,079
kind to the point of being ridiculous.

59
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,160
I want to be alone for a while.

60
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:36,000
I almost forgot about you.

61
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:40,759
But why do you

62
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:42,480
still show up in my life?

63
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,519
I had no childhood.

64
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,399
It's all your fault.

65
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,040
I hate you.

66
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,879
But now I've come to terms with it.

67
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,439
I'm grateful to you.

68
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:17,800
I've learned a lot.

69
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:22,360
I learned to cook for myself.

70
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,680
I learned to protect myself.

71
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:29,920
I learned to paint.

72
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:31,519
I learned to fight.

73
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,519
I'm good at it now.

74
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,639
No one can bully me.

75
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,519
After returning to the country,

76
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:50,080
I met two people.

77
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,759
His name is Jiang Yue.

78
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,000
We are very similar.

79
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,279
And a little girl.

80
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,559
Her name is Lu Qi.

81
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:04,960
If you

82
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,480
didn't run away so fast that day,

83
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:11,600
I would have introduced them to you.

84
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:26,480
3Z

85
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:28,840
is embroiled in a scandal

86
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,000
of mafia involvement.

87
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:32,200
Shuyun Hall is one of the 13 artists

88
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:33,919
who will be terminated.

89
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:37,279
Lin Chuanye said

90
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:38,919
his reputation has been affected,

91
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,919
and he won't cooperate with them anymore.

92
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,679
News from Duke County says

93
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,720
the boss has issued a hunting order for you.

94
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,559
Call Lu Qi

95
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:20,799
and ask her where Jiang Yue is.

96
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:21,879
I don't know.

97
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,759
You're her mother, don't you know?

98
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,159
How would I know?

99
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,519
Did you tell me?

100
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:28,600
How would I know?

101
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:30,080
What can I do

102
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,039
but wait?

103
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,000
Wait?

104
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,120
If I waited like you,

105
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,519
How do you think you became Mrs. Jiang?

106
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,679
Just waiting?

107
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,200
You went through so much to marry me.

108
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,320
Was Qi Qi's father

109
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:58,039
not killed by accident?

110
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:01,399
Sir.

111
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,519
Gao Qiao,

112
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,879
do you remember

113
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:21,080
who brought you back

114
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,240
when you were scrounging for scraps in the garbage?

115
00:11:26,159 --> 00:11:28,960
And who gave you your status and position today?

116
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,159
You can't betray me.

117
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,720
Just forget about ASO.

118
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:40,559
Bring Jiang Yue back.

119
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,000
It's the last time.

120
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:06,679
When you get better,

121
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,080
I'll go with you to collect folk songs.

122
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:10,879
That place is very beautiful.

123
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,000
You will like it.

124
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,360
♪Happiness is a pantomime.♪

125
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,000
♪Sadness♪

126
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,159
♪is a solo.♪
